Persistent Volumes:
-------------------
- Persistent Volumes retain even after the pods are deleted. 
- Persistent Volumes are the alternatives to volumes which are deleted along with pods

Procedure to connect persistent Volumes using CSI drivers are

AWS-EBS: (link: https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/aws-ebs-csi-driver)
--------
- Ensure to read the CSI-EBS driver documentation for all the specifications
- Install it using the documentation as specified in details
